data.text:
The EoDM are not death metal at all. They are polished garage rock made by Josh Homme (Queens of the Stone Age) and Jesse Hughes. This song is from their second album, Death by Sexy, which came out in 2006. The band has an awesome sense of humor to go with their awesome music, and all of their songs are worth checking out. Enjoy!
